  "body": "### Steps:\r\n1. Open a community where you are a member.\r\n2. Send some messages.\r\n3. Leave the community.\r\n4. Open the channel of the current community.\r\n5. Long-tap on your message.\r\n\r\n### Actual result:\r\nCommunity non-members see the following options in the drawer after the message is long-tapped:\r\n- Ability to react.\r\n- Edit message.\r\n- Pin/Unpin.\r\n- Delete for everyone.\r\n![image](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/52490791/4753f963-24fc-45a9-868f-a1bec682a21f)\r\n\r\n### Expected result:\r\nCommunity non-members should see the drawer as per the [design](https://www.figma.com/file/apCsJHT8J58JXbJD2igtbd/Context-Drawers-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=1-3573&mode=design&t=iq6aSpK2V9nagAdj-0), excluding the ability to show reactions. Reference to design team reply [here](https://discord.com/channels/624634427930312714/842696205213368331/1197485033309622332).\r\n\r\n### ENV:\r\nNightly [18 Jan 2024]\r\n",
